<plot>A TIGER in the DARK is a story based on true events. Its follows the exploits of one man as he aspires to accomplish the impossible. After countless failures he is ready to cave in and assume an ordinary role in society. Yet, by mere chance he encounters two individuals that show him just how powerful dreams can be. However, all soon starts to crumble as jealousy consumes former friends and allies. It isn't long until his choices inevitably alter his destiny and force him to leave all those he ever cared about behind. As time passes and stray thoughts of submitting to the anguish inside him overtake his rational, Drew Evans must once and for all find the courage to become what no one though the could.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?017197</url></doc>
